Articles.Content:
Here is a module manager configuration that will enable you to collect science from probes.

    @PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[ModuleCommand],#vesselType[Probe]]{	MODULE	{		name = ModuleScienceContainer		reviewActionName = Review Stored Data		storeActionName = Store Experiments		evaOnlyStorage = False		storageRange = 1.3	}}

